\n\nThe video is unrelated (from 2025), but it shows what it looks like when a ship that size is hit.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 2325}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZR8hpn2", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 23, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8568954, "raw_content": "All wars are from dictators.  They need an external enemy to stay in power.  People are willing to starve if there is an external enemy threat and dictators use that.\r\n\r\nEstablished democracies have never had a war against each other and never will.  The issues are internal.\r\n\r\nAmerica has the foreign policy mandate to spread democracy around the world which will be world peace.  In all cases we have taken that approach, except for Viet Nam where we assainated the democratic leader and put in the extremely unpopular local army. \r\n\r\nIn all cases that we have put in a democracy they are now our allies.  The Korean War was a failure yet compare North and South Korea today.  \r\n\r\nThere are only a few non democracies left in existence, this Axis of Fear, and Iran is one of them.  ", "author": "williammcfadden", "created": 1776647339369, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Voiceofreason72", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "There is only one solution to Iran -- Democracy.  Look at Japan, look at South Korea, look at Europe, look at Iraq, even Africa -- we are not at war with Democracies and never will be.   ", "last_comment_created": 1776651691025, "content": "<p>All wars are from dictators.  They need an external enemy to stay in power.  People are willing to starve if there is an external enemy threat and dictators use that.</p>\n<p>Established democracies have never had a war against each other and never will.  The issues are internal.</p>\n<p>America has the foreign policy mandate to spread democracy around the world which will be world peace.  In all cases we have taken that approach, except for Viet Nam where we assainated the democratic leader and put in the extremely unpopular local army.</p>\n<p>In all cases that we have put in a democracy they are now our allies.  The Korean War was a failure yet compare North and South Korea today.</p>\n<p>There are only a few non democracies left in existence, this Axis of Fear, and Iran is one of them.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 23, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZR7YtEo", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 323, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8567762, "raw_content": "", "author": "deletedandreacted", "created": 1776595618613, "profile_picture": "JmO8NAlGTAkJ", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "thelastlast", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.zerohedge.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZR7YtEo.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.zerohedge.com/political/spanberger-signs-unconstitutional-bill-strip-confederacy-linked-groups-tax-exempt-status", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Spanberger signs unconstitutional bill to strip Confederacy-linked